.TH "LIGHTNING-PAYMENT-RETRY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-payment-retry \- retry a payment by re-submitting a BOLT-11 invoice
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning payment-retry
.I bolt11
.RB [ --sat
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Re-submits a BOLT-11 invoice to the daemon for payment.
Useful for retrying a previously failed payment.
Use
.B --sat
to supply an amount for zero-amount invoices.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"payment_hash":"...","status":"complete|failed|pending",
 "amount_msat":N,"fee_msat":N,"destination":"..."}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-payment-status (1),
.BR lightning-payment-list (1)
